asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Snow Crash
description: With a coat of winter and eyes of fire, this goddess of fire and ice has a lineage dating back before ice age of ice ages.  Found bounding through snow and clouds in the icy regions of the north this ski bunny has won the snow olympics year after year melting her way to success.  Her winter coat blends into the snow and clouds to avoid detection, the only thing you will see is two red dots shining in on you like a beacon in the mist. Lore has it Snow Crash continues the name of her ancestors with pride after helping save hundreds of FLUF that were trapped by the annual giant snow avalanche of the north when trekking for their new island after the wreck, they were faced with the need for all 10,000 FLUF to cross the weakest part of the glacier, never before had so many fluff put this much weight on the crux.  The snow and ice had been weakened by the first 9,000 and as the remaining FLUF were only half way across the great glacier began to crack.  Snow Crash saw what was happening and positioned herself in the centre of the remaining few, as they were consumed by the biggest avalanche ever witnessed in history, swallowing them up like ice in a blender and burying them deep. Quickly and confidently Snow Crash used her eyes of fire melting air pockets so each FLUF could breath and dig themselves out with the help of the 9,000.  In fact, this matrix of now tunnels still remains to this day, known as The Warren Of Ice in the North and is used in the Winter Olympics for the underground bob sled races and other Red Bull high risk events.  Like all good snow bunnies, Snow Crash always brings good wybes.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---
